sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Envoy/Istio Gateway<br/>80-443/TCP
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker (EPP)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC ext-proc
    participant MS as Model Server Pods<br/>/metrics endpoint
    participant PDS as PD-Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP Proxy
    participant PF as Remote Prefiller Pod
    participant ENC as Remote Encoder Pod
    participant DEC as Local Decoder (vLLM)<br/>8001/TCP
    participant ZMQ as ZMQ KV-Cache Events<br/>5557/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,MS: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request (Non-Disaggregated)
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS at gateway<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (app-level)
        GW->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, TLS (self-signed)<br/>Request headers + body
        Note over EPP: Schedule: filter → score → pick<br/>Check KV-cache, queue depth,<br/>prefix affinity, LoRA affinity
        EPP-->>MS: HTTP GET /metrics<br/>Scrape KV-cache utilization,<br/>queue depth, running requests
        MS-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics response
        EPP-->>GW: ext-proc ProcessingResponse<br/>Set target endpoint header<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, TLS
        GW->>MS: Forward request to selected pod<br/>HTTP, target from EPP routing decision
        MS-->>GW: Inference response (streaming/non-streaming)
        GW-->>Client: JSON/SSE response
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Client,DEC: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D) via PD-Sidecar
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        GW->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, TLS
        Note over EPP: Schedule: select decode pod<br/>Set X-Prefill-Endpoint header<br/>to remote prefiller address
        EPP-->>GW: ext-proc response with<br/>target=decode pod,<br/>X-Prefill-Endpoint=prefiller addr
        GW->>PDS: Forward to PD-Sidecar on decode pod<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, 8000/TCP, TLS (optional)
        PDS->>PF: Dispatch prefill request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS (optional)<br/>Target from X-Prefill-Endpoint header
        PF-->>PDS: Prefill response with<br/>kv_transfer_params (NIXL/Mooncake/SGLang)
        Note over PDS: Inject kv_transfer_params<br/>into decode request body
        PDS->>DEC: Forward decode request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, 8001/TCP, TLS (optional)<br/>Body includes kv_transfer_params
        DEC-->>PDS: Decode response (streaming/non-streaming)
        PDS-->>GW: Forward response to gateway
        GW-->>Client: JSON/SSE response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,DEC: Flow 3: Encoder-Prefill-Decode (EPD) for Multimodal
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(multimodal payload)
        GW->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest
        EPP-->>GW: ext-proc response with targets
        GW->>PDS: Forward to PD-Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP
        PDS->>ENC: Fan-out encode requests<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS (optional)
        ENC-->>PDS: Encoder response with<br/>ec_transfer_params
        PDS->>PF: Dispatch prefill with<br/>ec_transfer_params + prompt<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS (optional)
        PF-->>PDS: Prefill response with<br/>kv_transfer_params
        PDS->>DEC: Forward decode with<br/>kv_transfer_params<br/>8001/TCP
        DEC-->>PDS: Decode response
        PDS-->>GW: Forward response
        GW-->>Client: JSON/SSE response
    end

    rect rgb(245, 245, 245)
        Note over EPP,ZMQ: Background: KV-Cache Event Subscription
        ZMQ-->>EPP: ZMQ PUB/SUB<br/>5557/TCP, TCP<br/>KV-cache block add/remove events
        Note over EPP: Update per-endpoint<br/>prefix cache state<br/>for exact prefix matching
    end
